ctrl + b +
[ vim mode (g to top )
% verticle split
" horizontal
o ,x to switch between pane and kill pane

c,& new window and kill window
0 1 2 n,p(prev),l(;last) to move through them 
(,),L to switch between session
:new to open new session
, to rename it

d to detach
? to help 
tmux ls 
tmux attach -t <target_name> 
tmux rename-session -t 0 <name>
tmux new -s <session_name>
tmux kill-session -t <session_name>
ctrl + c to exit top window ( any overlay / func) etc 
session preserved until the system reboot

## Advanced ones

  - $ rename current session
  - t clock
  - w select window from menu
  - s select session from menu  

